description:
While much is known about Cuba's involvement on the political stage of the 20th century, the fascinating Geography of this archipelago is often neglected. Therefore, in this video we will have a closer look into the various mountain ranges, ecoregions, keys and islets around Cuba. 

If you want to further support the work I am doing on this channel, you can now leave a small donation at my buy me a coffee page here:

https://buymeacoffee.com/FactSpark

3:55 The Ecoregions
